<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The addBcc() function does not have the second parameter 'name' , while addCc() and addTo() do have it .
Instead the name is internally set to ''.</p>

<p>For consistency &amp; usablities sake addBcc() should also get the extra name parameter.</p>

    </div>
